Rating: 2
I originally tasted a similar recipe a year ago, but could not track it down. When I tried this recipe, it definitely did not meet my expectations, so I jazzed it up a little. Instead of 1 1/2 tsp Old Bay, I used 2 1/2 teaspoons, plus 1/8 tsp black pepper, 1/8 tsp ground cayenne pepper, and 1 Tbsp fresh squeezed lemon juice. Much Better! I received lots of compliments.

Rating: 4
